      • createClassPath

        public static java.lang.String createClassPath(ClassPathUtils.IURLResolver resolver,
                                               java.lang.Class<?> anchorClass)
                                        throws java.io.IOException
        Create class path for an anchor class. This method checks were the anchor class resides, i.e. in a jar file or directory and returns it.
